Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:20.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}阿根！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:21.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:23.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}把这些菜给吕爷爷送过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:24.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:50.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:52.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我是小白老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:53.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我是翻译助教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:00:57.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}今天我们的课程是！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:00.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}什么东西是不可以吃的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:04.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}你画的这是什么呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:07.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}爷爷你不要妨碍我教学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:08.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}我只是路过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.20,0:01:12.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}咳，还是用实物来讲解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:13.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}它把道具吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:26.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}要好好听话知道么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:30.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这个不能吃哟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:30.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}为什么呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:34.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}因为不听话就不能和我们在一起了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:36.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}BIU......
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:37.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}不要委屈啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.87,0:01:38.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}饿了就来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我会给你吃好多好多木头哒!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:43.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}所以你要听话哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:44.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好~哒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:48.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}看来还是用投食来教育比较容易啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:49.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}这句不要翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:02.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:05.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}如果不要造成这么大的破坏就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:09.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}鲨鱼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:11.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}为什么会有鲨鱼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:13.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}唔？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.04,0:02:17.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不是鲨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:22.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好大啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:24.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是水妖么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:26.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是被大水吸引过来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}还是要把它带出村子吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:31.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}希望它能听懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:36.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}别过来啊！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:39.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:41.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这下闯祸了……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:44.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}快出来！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:55.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:17.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这个可以吃么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:19.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}对哦，这个可以吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:26.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}小黑你出来啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:27.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}今天的治疗结束了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:28.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}今天的治疗结束了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:28.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:29.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}BIU！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}可以哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:34.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:36.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}怎么样~调教的好吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:38.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}嗯〜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:40.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}多亏了黑咻呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:42.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这个可以吃么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:43.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}可…可以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:47.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}它一直在问么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好像出了点问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:51.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这个可以吃么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:53.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:56.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不过不能这样一直吃的啦……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:58.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}比丟！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:20.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}知道了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}吃太多会离不开一个地方噢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:23.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}怕怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:24.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}还有这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你别信啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:29.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}走远了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}看来只是路过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:36.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}诶！ ！ ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:39.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}刚才那就是小黑的能力么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:42.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}就是这样~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:43.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:44.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}好厉害..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}躺在床上也可以拿东西吃呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:50.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}比丢好像被吓呆了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:26.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:28.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}西南三百余里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:29.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}你确定是他？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}和你所描述的特征吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}表像上是冰系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:36.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}先去调查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}你们找他干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:42.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}我们去的第二天老君发布了天明珠的任务被完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:43.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}那怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:45.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}集谛听与玄离的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:47.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}谁能从他们手中夺取天明珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:48.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}老君可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}好吧那会是谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}谛听是老君的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:01.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}但玄离不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你的意思是天明珠是玄离拿走的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:05.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}六成可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:07.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}所以需要调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:10.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}但如果真的是玄离
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:12.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我们也不是他的对手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:14.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}硬抢从来都不是我的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:20.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}是因为武力值低么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:20.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}闭嘴
